    <mxCell id="takeaway_box" value="Deploy: one AWS account, one control-plane region (us-east-1), CDK v2.  No Postgres, no Redis, no SaaS.  Two inference surfaces share one credit pipeline + audit log: Bedrock Converse (Claude, us-east-1) and bedrock-mantle Responses (OpenAI GPT-5.x, cross-region).  Backend task role holds no iam:* / sts:AssumeRole — worst-case blast radius is bounded to Stratoclave&#39;s own box."
      style="rounded=1;fillColor=#E8F5E9;strokeColor=#2E7D32;strokeWidth=2;fontSize=12;fontStyle=1;fontColor=#1B5E20;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;"
      vertex="1" parent="1">
